                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I received this razor from the prisoner's mother in his presence, and this seal and key from Laws.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. WALLACE</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> These are mine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoners Defence.</hi> I took the razor to make a pop-gun stick with. I happened to notch it, and did not like to put it back again, so I sold it for 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; I took the seal as well—I did not have any lancet-case.</p>
